name: Arab World Research Source (EBSCO)
description: AWRS is a full-text database that delivers content in English and Arabic for researchers of the Middle East from scholarly journals, trade publications, industry profiles, country reports, conference papers, and more. Coverage includes major subject areas such as science, economics, business, technology, sociology, and humanities. **This database is currently in a trial period. Please send feedback about this database to jp172@nyu.edu **
